## CI pipeline shape

```
{{CI_PIPELINE_DIAGRAM}}
```

- **Layer order:** unit → integration → smoke. E2E + canary run post-merge / post-deploy.
- **Fail-fast:** lower-layer failure skips higher layers.
- **Parallelism:** {{PARALLELISM_PLAN}}
- **Budget:** <15 min total per PR.

