## Repo configuration

> Without these, the verification commands in each task are advisory. With them, CI is the gate.

### Branch protection (`main`)

- Required status checks: every job from `test.yml` (lint, per-service unit, per-service integration, smoke, E2E)
- Required PRs (no direct pushes)
- Require branches up-to-date before merging
- Require conversation resolution
- Required approving reviews: {{REQUIRED_REVIEWS}}
- Enforce on admins: {{ADMIN_ENFORCEMENT}}
- Canary status check is NOT required-to-merge (canary is a deploy gate, not a merge gate)

